org.sql: SELECT issues.* FROM issues INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = issues.project_id INNER JOIN versions ON versions.id = issues.fixed_version_id WHERE issues.fixed_version_id IS NOT NULL AND issues.project_id <> versions.project_id AND versions.sharing <> 'system' AND issues.fixed_version_id = 7

rewrites.sql: SELECT issues.* FROM issues INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = issues.project_id WHERE issues.fixed_version_id IS NOT NULL AND issues.fixed_version_id = 7
